";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"http://www.slidedeck.com/?p=12756\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:246:\"After a busy 2012 in which we shipped  32 updates, the SlideDeck team is geared up for a big 2013! And as we get ready for our first major releases of the year we want to hear from you. Tell us what you’d like to see make it into SlideDeck....\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Jason\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3734:\"<p><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-12758\" title=\"2013 SlideDeck Features\" src=\"http://assets-slidedeck2.s3.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/2013_features.png?9d7bd4\" alt=\"2013 SlideDeck Features\" width=\"285\" height=\"183\" />After a busy 2012 in which we shipped  <em><strong>32</strong><strong> updates</strong></em>, the SlideDeck team is geared up for a big 2013! And as we get ready for our first major releases of the year we want to hear from you. Tell us what you’d like to see make it into SlideDeck. We’ll use your feedback to help shape our roadmap and ensure that SlideDeck is the product you want and need.</p>\n<p>Of course, we have a few ideas of our own, and we have some exciting announcements about planned new features and functionality coming in the next few weeks. Stay tuned for more on that front.</p>\n<p>So what will SlideDeck look like in 2013? Help us define the future. Take a minute to fill out this one-field form with your comment or suggestion. We (Jason and Morgan) will review every one with our engineers (Dave, John and Jamie) and prioritize, scope and build out the ones that will make SlideDeck better.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://dtelepathy.zendesk.com/forums/20554367-feature-request\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-12757\" title=\"Help make SlideDeck Better\" src=\"http://assets-slidedeck2.s3.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/cta-btn.png?9d7bd4\" alt=\"Help make SlideDeck Better\" width=\"276\" height=\"51\" /></a><em>(Requires a login &#8211; if you don&#8217;t have access to SlideDeck 2 support, just leave a comment!)</em></p>\n<p><strong>Just to sweeten the pot a bit, we’ll give away three free copies of our <a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/premium-lenses-ee0f2/\">premium lens packs</a> to three lucky commenters. Just a little something to say thanks for the effort.</strong></p>\n<p>By the way, have you heard about <a href=\"http://www.dtelepathy.com/blog/dt-labs/changing-how-we-invent-apps-with-dt-labs\" target=\"_blank\">DT Labs</a>? It&#8217;s a place for you to help us determine the future design standards of the Web, and there&#8217;s even a sneak preview at what SlideDeck&#8217;s future could look like in there. <a href=\"http://dtelepathy.com/labs\" target=\"_blank\">Enter the Lab</a>, and become a Design Scientist!</p>\n<br/><br/><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/?utm_source=feed_ad&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=sd_blog\"><img src=\"//s3.amazonaws.com/assets-slidedeck2/wp-content/themes/slidedeck2/images/sd-rss.jpg?9d7bd4\" alt=\"Easily create AWESOME WordPress sliders - Get SlideDeck\" style=\"display:block;border:none;\"/></a><div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=saUqmEhSTGY:0wsTo9LLWIw:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=saUqmEhSTGY:0wsTo9LLWIw:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=saUqmEhSTGY:0wsTo9LLWIw:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=saUqmEhSTGY:0wsTo9LLWIw:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=saUqmEhSTGY:0wsTo9LLWIw:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=saUqmEhSTGY:0wsTo9LLWIw:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=saUqmEhSTGY:0wsTo9LLWIw:F7zBnMyn0Lo\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=saUqmEhSTGY:0wsTo9LLWIw:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/Slidedeck/~4/saUqmEhSTGY\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:91:\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/weigh-in-what-do-you-want-to-see-from-slidedeck-in-2013/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"40\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:86:\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/weigh-in-what-do-you-want-to-see-from-slidedeck-in-2013/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"Win/Win: SlideDeck and SiteGround Hosting\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/Slidedeck/~3/RH0UOvy14gs/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:92:\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/winwin-slidedeck-and-siteground-hosting/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 30 Jan 2013 13:20:10 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:8:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"News & Updates\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"SlideDeck 2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"hosting\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"siteground hosting\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"SlideDeck\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"wordpress hosting\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:7;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"WordPress Slider Plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"http://www.slidedeck.com/?p=12690\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:326:\"We’re excited to announce that SlideDeck is now a featured plugin for SiteGround Hosting WordPress users. What does this mean exactly? Now SiteGround users will be able to quickly and easily add SlideDeck to their default WordPress installations with a couple of clicks. SiteGround customers get easy access to SlideDeck,...\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Morgan\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3808:\"<p>We’re excited to announce that SlideDeck is now a featured plugin for SiteGround Hosting WordPress users. What does this mean exactly? Now SiteGround users will be able to quickly and easily add SlideDeck to their default WordPress installations with a couple of clicks. SiteGround customers get easy access to SlideDeck, and of course we get to introduce ourselves to a bunch of new WordPress site owners.</p>\n<p>Why <a href=\"http://www.siteground.com/index.htm?afcode=419559cef569bdfec620acbf1d67a05e\">SiteGround hosting</a> you ask? Because they’re good people, and working with friendly people is one of our top priorities. Plus they offer solid <a href=\"http://www.siteground.com/wordpress-hosting.htm?afcode=419559cef569bdfec620acbf1d67a05e\">hosting for WordPress</a> (among others) and have some unique features that are wins for any site owner:</p>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">Unique server security that keeps hacks isolated to affected accounts</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">Automatic updates to the latest WordPress versions</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">In-house created WordPress caching plugin (3 caching layers!)</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">Cloudflare CDN integration</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">Security monitoring and rapid upgrades</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">Across the board hardware updates</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">Multiple hosting packages that start as low as $3.95/month</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We also love that they’ve <a href=\"http://blog.siteground.com/coolest-feature/\">outlined their most popular features in infographics</a>. Much more enjoyable than lots of technical documents, PDFs and bulleted feature lists.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.morganbrown.co/\">Morgan</a> setup a new blog over on SiteGround after <a href=\"http://www.siteground.com/index.htm?afcode=419559cef569bdfec620acbf1d67a05e\">checking them out</a>. You might want to keep them in mind the next time you’re looking for hosting, too.</p>\n<p>Stay tuned for more news from SlideDeck. We’re just getting started.<strong id=\"internal-source-marker_0.6110795175191015\"> </strong></p>\n<h3>SiteGround&#8217;s Unique WordPress Caching</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.siteground.com/wordpress-hosting.htm?afcode=419559cef569bdfec620acbf1d67a05e\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" title=\"Siteground WordPress Caching\" src=\"http://www.siteground.com/fw/img/infographic_supercacherspeed.jpg\" alt=\"Siteground WordPress Caching\" width=\"560\" height=\"3320\" /></a></p>\n<br/><br/><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/?utm_source=feed_ad&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=sd_blog\"><img src=\"//s3.amazonaws.com/assets-slidedeck2/wp-content/themes/slidedeck2/images/sd-rss.jpg?9d7bd4\" alt=\"Easily create AWESOME WordPress sliders - Get SlideDeck\" style=\"display:block;border:none;\"/></a><div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=RH0UOvy14gs:Dt4-ic8kWIw:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=RH0UOvy14gs:Dt4-ic8kWIw:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=RH0UOvy14gs:Dt4-ic8kWIw:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=RH0UOvy14gs:Dt4-ic8kWIw:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=RH0UOvy14gs:Dt4-ic8kWIw:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=RH0UOvy14gs:Dt4-ic8kWIw:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=RH0UOvy14gs:Dt4-ic8kWIw:F7zBnMyn0Lo\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=RH0UOvy14gs:Dt4-ic8kWIw:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/Slidedeck/~4/RH0UOvy14gs\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/winwin-slidedeck-and-siteground-hosting/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:83:\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/winwin-slidedeck-and-siteground-hosting/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		